  "description": "Gogs is an open source self-hosted Git service. Prior to 0.14.3, Git smart HTTP authorizes POST \u2026/git-receive-pack using the client-supplied service query string (so ?service=git-upload-pack is evaluated as read access) while routing still runs git receive-pack, allowing push where only read should be allowed. This vulnerability is fixed in 0.14.3.",
